    "prompt": "Resolve the pending ranged weapon or ammunition attack first: as the attack hits or misses, transform the weapon or ammunition into a lightning bolt, resolve scaled 4d8 Lightning damage on hit or half on miss, return the weapon or ammunition to normal form, then separately resolve the 10-foot Dexterity-save burst for nearby creatures.",
